"I'm actually married." There are multiple possibilities, I guess.

528
00:44:39,640 --> 00:44:41,190
But forget all those options.

529
00:44:41,190 --> 00:44:44,800
Yoon Dong Yoon's answer was the worst of the worst.

530
00:44:46,150 --> 00:44:49,220
"I'll pretend I didn't hear that."

