00:46:38,390 --> 00:46:40,060
I wasn't asking you to ask that.

554
00:46:40,060 --> 00:46:42,550
Maybe it's my opinion that you need?

555
00:46:47,260 --> 00:46:49,600
I want to applaud you.

556
00:46:50,940 --> 00:46:54,040
He isn't your pair.

557
00:46:54,040 --> 00:46:56,490
Not only does he have nothing,

558
00:46:56,490 --> 00:46:59,350
but he also has neither guts nor courage.

559
00:47:00,100 --> 00:47:03,980
He was just too naïve, like a little puppy.

560
00:47:03,980 --> 00:47:08,180
Goodness, this isn't a spot for someone so carefree.

561
00:47:08,180 --> 00:47:10,890
I said I broke up with him.

562
00:47:11,940 --> 00:47:13,630
Is there a need to be so harsh?

563
00:47:13,630 --> 00:47:18,140
Do you think I'm only talking about Hyeon Ho right now?

