00:54:16,450 --> 00:54:19,540
By chance, I didn't wake you, did I?

646
00:54:19,540 --> 00:54:21,730
 No, not at all. 

647
00:54:23,410 --> 00:54:25,900
Why are you still outside?

648
00:54:25,900 --> 00:54:28,440
 I'm just having a walk. 

649
00:54:30,270 --> 00:54:32,200
It's not for any bad reason.

650
00:54:32,200 --> 00:54:36,450
It's just...the weather was nice.

651
00:54:38,570 --> 00:54:43,770
Where are you? Are you at the palace again?

652
00:54:43,770 --> 00:54:45,510
How did you know?

653
00:54:45,510 --> 00:54:49,670
I'm walking the Deoksu Palace stonewall walkway.

654
00:54:49,670 --> 00:54:51,710
Oh really?

655
00:54:51,710 --> 00:54:55,940
You mean to tell me you're walking there alone at this hour?

656
00:54:55,940 --> 00:54:59,040
Well, of course, I'm walking here alone. Who else would I walk with?

657
00:55:09,830 --> 00:55:12,980
Then, get home safely.

658
00:55:12,980 --> 00:55:15,550
- Song Ah! 
 - Yes? 

659
00:55:20,210 --> 00:55:23,850
By chance, do you have any plans after work tomorrow?

660
00:55:23,850 --> 00:55:25,680
No.

661
00:55:27,010 --> 00:55:28,630
 Oh that's good... 

662
00:55:28,630 --> 00:55:33,710
Th-then...would you like to have dinner with me?

663
00:55:35,370 --> 00:55:38,810
Yes. I'd like that.

664
00:55:38,810 --> 00:55:42,630
Then...I'll see you tomorrow.

665
00:55:42,630 --> 00:55:44,560
Yes.

666
00:55:44,560 --> 00:55:46,710
Good night.

667
00:55:47,830 --> 00:55:50,100
You too, Joon Young.

