672
00:56:54,450 --> 00:56:58,810
 It is with regret that, despite your wonderful audition and interview, 

673
00:56:58,810 --> 00:57:02,720
 we have decided to move forward with a different candidate. 

674
00:57:14,530 --> 00:57:16,430
Song Ah!

675
00:57:25,470 --> 00:57:27,800
Did you wait long?

676
00:57:27,800 --> 00:57:29,700
Oh, not at all.

677
00:57:31,710 --> 00:57:33,840
Shall we get something to eat?

678
00:57:33,840 --> 00:57:35,520
Yes.

679
00:57:48,500 --> 00:57:51,160
Then you must have been busy all day.

680
00:57:51,160 --> 00:57:54,330
It was fine because I didn't have to stay overtime.

681
00:57:54,330 --> 00:57:58,080
What did you do today Joon Young?

682
00:57:58,080 --> 00:58:02,880
Oh, I just had some personal business to take care of.

683
00:58:05,060 --> 00:58:06,720
I see...

684
00:58:09,810 --> 00:58:12,510
Should we walk some?

685
00:58:12,510 --> 00:58:14,160
Yes!

686
00:58:16,470 --> 00:58:18,730
I was right after all.

687
00:58:18,730 --> 00:58:20,340
About what?

688
00:58:20,340 --> 00:58:25,640
I thought if I saw you, I'd feel better.

689
00:58:26,580 --> 00:58:29,440
Did something happen today?

690
00:58:30,880 --> 00:58:34,720
I don't know why I think of you during difficult days.

