00:58:36,770 --> 00:58:40,150
You must be tired of me. I'm sorry.

692
00:58:40,150 --> 00:58:42,450
It's okay.

693
00:58:42,450 --> 00:58:47,910
But still...it would be better if you didn't have hard times.

694
00:58:49,600 --> 00:58:52,970
You should also call me during hard days too.

695
00:58:54,450 --> 00:58:59,110
For me... I think I'll call you when I'm feeling good.

696
00:58:59,110 --> 00:59:01,700
That's even better. Don't forget!

697
00:59:01,700 --> 00:59:03,300
Okay.

698
00:59:04,350 --> 00:59:06,170
Promise...

